Let's go.

00:00:34.085 --> 00:00:37.205
First up, are your typography
skills outside of white space?

00:00:37.265 --> 00:00:43.025
Text takes up the most real estate on
your website, but 99% of web designers

00:00:43.085 --> 00:00:47.795
can't tell the difference between bad
